      <textAnnotation id="sid-4EC9DC39-BB46-4762-92CB-9F7371F01FAE" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>-Supplier.intel.com(New Supplier asking to work with intel)
-SCheck/Preferred Supplier (Existing suppliers)
-Industry Workgroups
-CM/Market Insight 
-Sourcing Core Team(External research)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B8DDA120-4322-40E3-B6AA-5216C1E6B4FF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>- Allows Identification of New Suppliers meeting qualifications required for intel Specifications </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: PTP - Procure To Pay
Process Group: PM - Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-050 Identify Potential New Suppliers</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-23F82949-1ECA-4BB9-9669-A7F82648A52A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description-
Determine which suppliers have the ability to fulfill the identified specifications or scope of work.  Use all referenced sources, in-house experiences, such as:
- System purchasing database for previous purchases of similar terms or services
- Informational databases (non-system)
- Solicitation of references from employees
- Solicitation of references from industry sources, networked contacts</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6E017A3C-63FB-43A8-AE61-41934D9897BF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
